            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1670926963851-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have browned, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add the <strong>walnut paste </strong>to the pan with your<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground fenugreek</strong> (not a fan of fenugreek? Only add a little!) and 2/3<strong> </strong>of<strong> </strong>your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for a further 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle more oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670926971553-x200.jpg",
