      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> creamy walnut mushroom satsivi </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and <strong>quick-pickled shallot salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
